{"about_the_game":"Gob, a classic RPG slime, finds himself in a predicament when he stumbles upon a &quot;Hero&quot; slaying innocent people and other slimes in the pursuit of the Goblet Eternal. When the hero realizes he's been spotted committing his crimes, he chases Gob through dangerous terrain wielding his deadly sword. The &quot;Hero&quot; will stop at nothing to silence Gob for what he has seen, but Gob is cunning and won't be caught easily.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mechanics</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Jump </strong>over gaps, obstacles, enemies, spikes and more<br></li><li><strong>Slide </strong>under tight spaces and deadly things<br></li><li><strong>Spring </strong>on springboards to reach otherwise unreachable places</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hazards</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dehydration </strong>in the desert is real. Find pools of water to rehydrate Gob along his journey<br></li><li><strong>Sandstorms </strong>in the desert will surely kill Gob unless he can outrun them<br></li><li><strong>Falling </strong>off cliffs is a real risk<br></li><li><strong>Blizzards </strong>can blow Gob into spikes or off of cliffs in snow worlds<br></li><li><strong>Snow and ice squalls</strong> can be deadly unless Gob can outrun them<br></li><li><strong>Classic </strong> platformer mechanics such as falling platforms, moving platforms, spinning platforms, traps and switches are also standing in the way of victory</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1620342597","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564240/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1620342597","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1620342597","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1620342597","categories":[{"descri